---
title: Mexican-Inspired Pork Stew with Tortilla Chips
description: Packed with hearty and delicious pork and veggies, this Mexican stew is the perfect remedy to a long work week. Crushed tortilla chips and a dollop of lime crema offer a pop of flavour, perfect for finishing off this bowl of goodness.
